					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10290025#post-4222140</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10290025/scp-4221#post-4222140</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2019 22:48:01 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>The guardian child</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>3453371</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>Subject showed a consistent aversion to the number seven&#8230;</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>Subject showed consistently sorted red cards into their own stack, separating them from all other shades.</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>&#8230;a puddle of vivid red liquid seeps from under the door.</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>On the floor are six skeletons.</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>They are evenly spaced in a radial pattern, with an empty spot indicating an absent seventh figure.</p> </blockquote> <blockquote> <p>On the pedestal is a large oaken door and frame with seven locks.</p> </blockquote> <p>&#8230;&#8230;this is connected to the scarlet king, isn't it.</p> <p>Too many references to be a coincidence.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
