					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10290025#post-4151402</guid>
				<title>Very Intriguing</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-10290025/scp-4221#post-4151402</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 12 Feb 2019 21:55:02 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Holly Nightmare</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>4247157</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is one of those skips where I'm left wondering&#8230; what exactly is the explanation for all this? But I like that a lot - the mystery draws me in. I just kind of wish I knew more, in terms of where SCP-4221-1 came from, and something more of its relationship with SCP-4221-2. But it was definitely a good start, and I thought it was solid. +1</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
